y for learning. People are equally enthusiastic and dedicated to take on these challenges and in turn coming out with flying colours. You get respect from colleagues and get ample freedom to take initiatives, own decisions. We set bold targets for ourselves and leave no stone unturned to achieve them as well. Great to be part of this winning team of Rockman !&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1732536703733-6&#8243;][testimonial image=&#8221;2568&#8243; star_rating=&#8221;none&#8221; title=&#8221;Testimonial&#8221; id=&#8221;1732536703830-0&#8243; name=&#8221;Mr. Navneet&#8221; subtitle=&#8221;Associate (serving since last 30 Yrs)&#8221; quote=&#8221;Working at Rockman is my Family Legacy, My father used to work here and now I. I really enjoy my work &amp; feel proud to be part of such organization.&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1732536703831-0&#8243;][testimonial image=&#8221;361&#8243; add_image_shadow=&#8221;true&#8221; star_rating=&#8221;none&#8221; title=&#8221;Testimonial&#8221; id=&#8221;1732536703904-2&#8243; name=&#8221;Mr. Arvind Pandey&#8221; subtitle=&#8221;Deputy Manager (Staff) (serving since last 12Yrs)&#8221; quote=&#8221;It\u2019s a great organization with well equipped &amp; latest technology. Also the vision of our management is to take each and every employee in the success journey and also take care of individual\u2019s respect&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1732536703905-1&#8243;][testimonial image=&#8221;364&#8243; add_image_shadow=&#8221;true&#8221; star_rating=&#8221;none&#8221; title=&#8221;Testimonial&#8221; id=&#8221;1732536703958-5&#8243; name=&#8221;Mr. Devender&#8221; subtitle=&#8221;Office Boy (Associate) (serving since last 22 Yrs)&#8221; quote=&#8221;Individual\u2019s respect &amp; good behavior of Sr. People here at Rockman, motivates me. Also, we get salary on time. I have established my family due to Rockman. It\u2019s a good Organization to work with.&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1732536703959-4&#8243;][testimonial image=&#8221;367&#8243; add_image_shadow=&#8221;true&#